#.python-version

# pipenv
#   According to pypa/pipenv#598, it is recommended to include Pipfile.lock in version control.
#   However, in case of collaboration, if lock is generated on different OS, it could fail.
#Pipfile.lock

# poetry
#   Reference: https://python-poetry.org/docs/basic-usage/#commit-your-poetrylock-to-version-control
